description: This bright and colorful family-owned truck is one of the best spots in Pittsburgh for its sweet & savory selection of high-quality crepes, including…The Veggie Omelette Crepe (filled with fresh tomato, spinach, mozzarella cheese, and basil sauce)The Classic Nutella Crepe (filled with scrumptious Nutella, peanut butter, a sprinkle of powdered sugar, and a dollop of delightful whipped cream)(and many more!)These fantastically tasty folded treats are perfect for every kind of occasion, so if you need to feed your guests at your next event, be sure to invite PGH Crepes!
name: PGH Crepes
